race.comment: CHEF'S DREAM (3) recorded a half a length win (30.68) in a Grade 5 last time at this track. Makes strong appeal on best. BISCOTTI BLAST (7) pinged the lids from out wide but run ended and faded out of it late when 6th at this track in Grade 5 company. Solid record here at the distance winning five races. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Worth following up. NOW SEE HERE (1) was out of the frame here most recently but can atone. Something for the Multiples: WEST ON COLE (4)
